  "texts": [
    "Although the use of a FoV restrictor could reduce such effects, such framerate jitter will be more noticeable on medium and low-end graphics hardware.",
    "Therefore, we encourage future work to investigate the integration of further optimization techniques, such as foveated rendering, to enable a comfortable VR NeRF system even on low-end graphics devices.",
    "It is also important to note that the field of photorealistic view synthesis is evolving rapidly.",
    "Relevant work on representing real-world scenes with 3D Gaussian functions as an alternative to multi-layer perceptron has emerged in the last 2 months, paving the way for more efficient rendering of radiance fields via rasterization rather than ray marching (Kerbl et al., 2023).",
    "We encourage future work to further extend our system to support 3D Gaussian splatting in immersive VR (Kerbl et al., 2023), and to compare the different trade-offs between the two types of representation and rendering for user interaction and system performance."
  ],
